{"tid":125351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"JJ 放入碳酸水  勃起力會升級  日本正太親身體驗","createTime":"2017-02-18T11:47:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T05:31:21.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"33c99d03d43863283d8251ba0adc9aeb7bc38644","tid":125351,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T11:47:37.000Z","msg":"【GG片】日本正太親身體驗　「老二放入碳酸水」<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170217/1057890\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Flife%2F20170217%2F1057890&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=d227f8d0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170217/1057890</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">最近網路上瘋傳一張把「雞雞放到碳酸水裡，勃起力會升級」的圖片，據說習慣刺激後可自由自在地控制發射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，而現在竟然有人真的做了實驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n片：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rDfqZaE8TYI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrDfqZaE8TYI&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=cbaa5566\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rDfqZaE8TYI</a><br />\n<br />\n據《日本集合》了解，一名濃眉大眼，長相清秀的日本男生，因為看到了這張圖片而好奇地想親身做實驗，影片中只見他先將注意事項唸出來，再把事先準備好的碳酸水倒進杯子裡，最後雙手雙腳撐地，慢慢地把自己的老二放到杯子裡，但沒多久，他突然跳起，並且雙手握住自己的老二似乎想減緩疼痛感，過一陣子後，再對著鏡頭表示自己的感想，並語重心長地宣告實驗失敗。<br />\n<br />\n但台灣男性學醫學會秘書長、耕莘醫院泌尿科主治醫師廖峻厚接受《蘋果日報》訪問時表示，將男性生殖器泡入碳酸水，可能只是藉由酸度與氣泡刺激，來降低龜頭敏感度。但這種方法，目前沒有任何學理依據，小弟弟泡入糖水的風險也是未知，建議民眾還是不要擅自嘗試。<br />\n<br />\n看完影片的網友開玩笑地說「把小弟弟裹粉放入熱油鍋裡面試試看，能不能提高勃起力我不知道，但是小弟弟會變得金黃酥脆」、「可以找菜阿嘎來親身體驗這個過程嗎？」、「之前有美國人把沙拉油注射進陰莖裡，結果導致海綿體結痂，終生無法勃起」、「冰火五重天的冰水換成可樂，那麼男生不就立馬倒陽！」、「噴肌樂快又有效」、「乾脆放在水泥裡，保證每天都是硬化。」、「哈哈，真的GG了吧！」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"7ea9b2f59a3a2b06aab599f7bd7f79542a003af2","tid":125351,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T11:49:48.000Z","msg":"咁渣ga"},{"pid":"33539b0f8fd3134c761d4e590e48ab4c225b5ff2","tid":125351,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e451f9d433bfa36f23c38ad1d7f3805106f288dc","tid":125351,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T04:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e078c7765d37c0e5f41ab1ba0e9ab3a4aceab9c3","tid":125351,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:27:34.000Z","msg":"今次仲唔到我做仆街仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5bfb526e8f324d00e6c131cddc92b94d128753","tid":125351,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:31:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今次仲唔到我做仆街仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恭喜你做到jj插炭酸水嘅仆街仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}